# BFF & Bedrock (Hard Rule)

- Client never calls AWS/Bedrock. All LLM via Next.js **`/api/chat`** only.
- `/api/chat`: Supabase server client (`@supabase/ssr`), session from cookies. `!session` → 401 immediately; do not call Bedrock. Use `streamText` and `return stream.toDataStreamResponse()`. Accept canvas (nodes, edges) in body; pure `parseCanvasState(nodes, edges): string` for LLM context; no classes/mutation.
- AWS/Bedrock env vars server-only (no `NEXT_PUBLIC_`); frontend must not see or send them.
